Text: Donations as of Jan to date it looks like were just over Way to go Thank you to everybody that has contacted Michael and I regarding donations Im attaching the main spreadsheet that details all of the donations that have been reported to date This should give you a good idea of where were at Please take a look at it if you have any comments please let me know We have not heard from a few of you yet and rumor has it that there are still a few donations that havent been reported to us Please email me or phone us by Tuesday with the name and amount of the expected donation and we will ensure they get proper credit in the brochure etc Regards Kelly Trout and Michael Leahy OGC Cheques xls
